
nowa api spec

KnowledgeItem
  ( rw:title, r:created, r:url )
  - save
  - words
  - tags
  - status (message)
  - source (downloaded)
  - id
  - reload

User
  ( email )
  * login
  * logout
  * knowledge_items
  * find_by_id (future)
  * create_knowledge_item
  X tags
  


